reviews.review_text:
This recording is one of my top 5 all time favourites 
 This is a really fine recording .

 A friend got a copy of this very same lineage in April 1993 , made me a copy .  And since ive gone through - worn out - about 5 or 6 copies of it .

 Im glad i found it in this format , as this Sennheiser rig captured some awesome sounds that spring night at the Rose .  A fine example where the audience tape is levels higher / above ( in quality overall ] , than a mixing desk recording .  Congrats Mr Leitzenberger on such a nice tape
